Megatron Revived:
 
Megatron nodded his head in agreement.
"Yes, an new ally to help us fight against the Predacons once we dispose of Unicron," he said.
The Emperor clone's sensors reported, that in a few hours the interferance would dissolve.
"In a few decacycles that interferance will disappear.  Shall we try then?"
